s://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/57569457_372835095485871_3124097249015020700_n.png?_nc_cat=103&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=JApTg6dV4SEQ7kNvgFOOFuP&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&_nc_gid=A4VnG6HfppPiXrb6IsLhpaw&oh=00_AYCO0q5msXPXNICYyFCXzdEkeb3XthV9mtJbTeE8D-UOMg&oe=66CF1B13"}, {"file_name": "Recording Radial Pulse Simulator_SS_05.png", "id": "837151848339615", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/43931336_837151851672948_3791241212278429846_n.png?_nc_cat=101&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=T8S_ELkDbNIQ7kNvgF7Swbe&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&_nc_gid=A4VnG6HfppPiXrb6IsLhpaw&oh=00_AYCX9Zwur4YaJp595dT1gDBinA1mWLNPGMlYM96V_gjZwQ&oe=66CF0E27"}], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": {"file_name": "2560X1440.png", "id": "3812821238933502", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38982527_3812821242266835_422188521434867194_n.png?_nc_cat=102&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=ep6AztA54VYQ7kNvgGQuvRw&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&_nc_gid=A4VnG6HfppPiXrb6IsLhpaw&oh=00_AYBD_xfz6e5cCyliEiKnNxwO-nwjcGSN2pQwy76aJu5meg&oe=66CEF40C"}, "display_name": "Recording Radial Pulse Simulator", "keywords": [], "long_description": "This tutorial covers the essential steps for measuring and recording a patient's radial pulse. It includes preparation, locating the pulse, measurement, and documentation. By the end of this tutorial, learners will be able to: \n\nRemember the key steps in recording a radial pulse. \n- Understand the significance of pulse measurement in patient assessment. \n- Apply the correct techniques to ensure accurate pulse recording. \n- Analyze pulse data to detect any irregularities. \n- Evaluate their measurement accuracy and identify areas for improvement. \n- Create precise and thorough patient records based on their findings. \n\nThis comprehensive approach ensures CNAs are well-prepared to assist patients with feeding efficiently and compassionately in real-world clinical settings. ", "short_description": "Develop prof